### 9. 请写出求斐波那契数列任意一位的值的算法

```csharp
static int Fn(int n)
{
    if (n <= 0)
    {
        throw new ArgumentOutOfRangeException();
    }
    if (n == 1 || n == 2)
    {
        return 1;
    }
    return checked(Fn(n - 1) + Fn(n - 2)); // when n>46 memory will overflow
}
```

